    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/31092fd49ffe573aa0f5f9f843e1c871.webp?t=1768806536\" width=200 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在海洋中探索，由浅入深，从光华瑰丽到无光深渊，打造更坚实的潜水服，一路深潜，感受不同深度海洋的不同景观，与各异的海洋生物一同探索埋藏的奥秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/de2b4bfd3d643ff4ae705fcc07fefbfa.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/de2b4bfd3d643ff4ae705fcc07fefbfa.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/de2b4bfd3d643ff4ae705fcc07fefbfa.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/2d24b0fca2bc28e1d8748b7c7b9e93e5.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/2d24b0fca2bc28e1d8748b7c7b9e93e5.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/2d24b0fca2bc28e1d8748b7c7b9e93e5.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/bf66af52680960192aa35e65b7418d32.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/bf66af52680960192aa35e65b7418d32.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/bf66af52680960192aa35e65b7418d32.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/d3675778bb89a6d1da838ed4e68eff67.webp?t=1768806536\" width=200 height=27 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过采集和战斗获得素材，生产各式各样的武器，配合各种“嵌入式生体”，打造出最适合你的强力武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/7cb5d9ccdeb82f0baaedc8fa59dedb22.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/7cb5d9ccdeb82f0baaedc8fa59dedb22.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/7cb5d9ccdeb82f0baaedc8fa59dedb22.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/da439708d664e958bae2c9de73ca17b6.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/da439708d664e958bae2c9de73ca17b6.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/da439708d664e958bae2c9de73ca17b6.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/dc92e739681bf223630c7a04d75f3276.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/dc92e739681bf223630c7a04d75f3276.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/dc92e739681bf223630c7a04d75f3276.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/f1e9fa16c6adb71b0d4ac1b9bbc85d7e.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/f1e9fa16c6adb71b0d4ac1b9bbc85d7e.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/f1e9fa16c6adb71b0d4ac1b9bbc85d7e.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/9b4f2031156ebd9cc3426f2aa12e214b.webp?t=1768806536\" width=200 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未知的深渊中危机四伏，诡异的巨兽阻拦在少女面前，击败巨兽，将其化作新的武器一路向前。伶俐的虎鲸、狂野的史前海兽、前所未见的怪异海怪，等着你来击败。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/d49e180c38d4d18d817c4a24700bbd83.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/d49e180c38d4d18d817c4a24700bbd83.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/d49e180c38d4d18d817c4a24700bbd83.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/2dee681cedb0b59e0d80f04b4a680916.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/2dee681cedb0b59e0d80f04b4a680916.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/2dee681cedb0b59e0d80f04b4a680916.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/f7a7b4882add3d021d17d5746fd18884.poster.avif?t=1768806536\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/f7a7b4882add3d021d17d5746fd18884.webm?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/f7a7b4882add3d021d17d5746fd18884.mp4?t=1768806536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222720/extras/98b7c7fca97c2840561f960723bfacfd.webp?t=1768806536\" width=200 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >广袤的海洋为何毫无人类的踪迹？本不该存在的生物为何出现在海底？少女肩负何种沉重的使命？深渊之下到底隐藏着何等秘密？等着你来和少女一同揭开。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想进一步了解《蜃海》以及犀鸟工作室，获得第一手的新鲜信息，请加入我们官方社群。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ群：976679462</p>",
